    &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.mahout&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;mahout-core&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;0.9&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

When 0.10.0 will be released, you will need to use

    &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.mahout&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;mahout-mrlegacy&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;0.10.0&lt;/version&gt;
