    while (!Thread.currentThread().isInterrupted()) {

and then you would shutdown the pool with:

    listenerThreadPool.shutdownNow();

I tend to poll for a couple of seconds or so and check for interrupt and then poll again if the clients aren&#39;t interruptible.

